@startuml
title State Diagram (Part 2): Environment and Rendering

top to bottom direction

[*] --> LightingSet : continued from Part 1

LightingSet --> EnvironmentApplied : EnvironmentHandler.applyHDRI(path)
EnvironmentApplied --> ControlsInitialized : OrbitControlsHandler.initialize()
ControlsInitialized --> ReadyToRender : System ready

ReadyToRender --> Rendering : render()
Rendering --> FrameRendered : onFrameComplete()
FrameRendered --> ReadyToRender

note right of FrameRendered
Loop continues while app is running
end note

ReadyToRender --> [*] : App Closed / Exit

@enduml
